{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9bffa0d290","title":"转发邓小平、彭真关于调查农村人民公社几个问题来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"67ac04f2cd","index":0,"year":1961,"month":5,"day":13,"articleId":"9bffa0d290"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bd9678625","name":"邓小平","type":"人物"},{"id":"5fd56865b0","name":"彭真","type":"人物"},{"id":"6316680b8e","name":"张平化","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""},{"id":"maoquanji44","name":"毛泽东全集第44卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/44-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3292dde56f","type":"title","text":"转发邓小平、彭真关于调查农村人民公社几个问题来信的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9bffa0d290"},{"id":"8d6f84e6cd","type":"authors","text":"毛泽东","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9bffa0d290"},{"id":"0ea4d8b659","type":"paragraph","text":"此信发给各中央局，各省、市、区党委，供参考。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9bffa0d290"},{"id":"d9446942be","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东1961年5月13日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9bffa0d290"}],"page":{"id":"bfc77ad09e","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"9bffa0d290","start":0,"end":0}},"maoquanji44":{"comments":[{"id":"2f743830f9","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"9bffa0d290","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"张平化（1907—2001），湖南哪县（今炎陵人）。当时任中共湖南省委第一书记。"},{"id":"fcdcbcc5a1","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"9bffa0d290","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指张平化1961年5月13日给毛泽东的信。这封信汇报了他到一个生产大队作调查，同群众商量解决按劳分配和经营管理方面存在的问题的情况。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2f743830f9","type":"paragraph","text":"此信转发各中央局，省、市、区党委，供参考。张平化同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"9bffa0d290"},{"id":"7a23c9cd97","type":"paragraph","text":"1961年5月14日，于天津","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"9bffa0d290"},{"id":"e3c488319a","type":"title","text":"给张平化\"的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"9bffa0d290"},{"id":"e5f965a5b3","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"9bffa0d290"},{"id":"fcdcbcc5a1","type":"paragraph","text":"你的这封信，可发湖南全省各地、市、县、社觉委研究，仿照办理。都要坚决走群众路线，一切问题都要和群众商量，然后共同决定，作为政策贯彻执行。各级党委，不许不作调查研究工作。绝对禁止党委少数人不作调查，不同群众商量，关在房子里，作出害死人的主观主义的所谓政策。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"9bffa0d290"}],"page":{"id":"3e74fe2823","publicationId":"maoquanji44","articleId":"9bffa0d290","start":281,"end":281}}}},"__N_SSG":true}